        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>A Just Society: The Mercy In Re-entry Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits the denial of federal public benefits to an individual solely on the basis of that individual's criminal conviction (whether under federal, state, tribal, or foreign law).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
